✅ Method: Clone → Change Remote → Push

1️⃣ Original repo clone cheyyandi
git clone https://github.com/SaikumarBandigi/SpringBootJune.git
cd SpringBootJune
2️⃣ Current remote check cheyyandi
git remote -v

👉 Output lo original repo untundi

3️⃣ Mee GitHub lo new empty repo create cheyyandi

Example:
👉 https://github.com/your-username/springboot-project

4️⃣ Remote change cheyyandi (important step)
git remote remove origin
git remote add origin https://github.com/your-username/springboot-project.git
5️⃣ Push to your GitHub
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main

🔥 Alternative (Single Command Method)

Direct ga mirror push cheyyachu:

git clone --mirror https://github.com/SaikumarBandigi/SpringBootJune.git
cd SpringBootJune.git
git push --mirror https://github.com/your-username/springboot-project.git
